These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, light-blue, white, coral
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, pakistani, nigerian, thai
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, milk, fanta
4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, poker, mah-jongg
 1. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 2. the person playing bridge is not to the left of the person playing bridge##8
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 5. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8
 6. the nigerian is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person who likes mauve##5
 8. the thai is between the person playing scrabble and the person drinking water##2
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is the nigerian##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
11. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the spanish##3
12. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5
13. the nigerian is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
14. the person who likes light-blue is the person playing poker##1
15. the person who likes light-blue is not the person drinking water##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Color         | mauve     | light-blue   | coral | white |
| Nationality   | pakistani | thai   | spanish   | nigerian  |
| Beverage         | water  | milk  | fanta  | sprite |
| Game     | bridge    | poker | scrabble     | mah-jongg    |

