.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, mechanic, entrepreneur, police-officer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, chaman, alhambra, cain
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, dancing, traveling
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, skateboard, subway
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
 2. the mechanic is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
 3. the mechanic is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
 4. the dressmaker is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
 6. the cain-smoker is not to the right of the police-officer##8
 7. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 8. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person driving the ship##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
11. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
12. the police-officer is on the left of the mechanic##1
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
15. the dressmaker is on the far left or far right##3
16. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
17. the dressmaker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
18. the chaman-smoker is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
19. the police-officer is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Job      | dressmaker | entrepreneur | police-officer  | mechanic  |
| Cigar          | cain     | chaman | prince | alhambra  |
| Hobby   | filmmaking    | dancing  | traveling | drawing |
| Transport           | skateboard | subway | quad-bike    | ship  |

