.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
City: colone, rome, nizza, new-york
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, lemon, apple, cherry
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, bird, frog
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, tiparillo, cain, pall-mall
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to nizza##5
 3. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person eating cherry##5
 4. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
 5. the cain-smoker is not to the right of the person eating strawberry##8
 6. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the person eating apple##8
 7. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
12. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| City         | colone    | new-york   | nizza | rome |
| Food   | strawberry     | apple  | cherry   | lemon      |
| Pet   | ferret | goldfish    | bird      | frog       |
