 9. the person playing poker is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
10. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the modern house##8
11. the person who likes light-blue is between the vegafina-smoker and the wooden house##2
12. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who likes white##1
13. the person playing whist is not to the right of the wooden house##8
