 3. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
 4. the person watching spy movies is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 5. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
 6. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the right of the person eating onion##8
 9. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person who growsrose and the person driving the helicopter##7
10. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
11. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
12. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
13. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
14. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
