 7. the montecristo-smoker is not to the left of the prince-smoker##8
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the goldfish##7
 9. the person eating mango is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the person eating pomegranate##8
11. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
12. the person eating spinach is on the far right##1
13. the montecristo-smoker is the owner of the rat##1
14. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person traveling to new-york##8
