 6. the person driving the helicopter is the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
 8. the colonial house is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 9. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the wooden house##1
11. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
13. the gothic-revival house is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
14. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
15. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's birthday is in november##1
16. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Transport           | subway | snowmobile       | ship      | helicopter  |
| Birthday   | september    | november | february   | january   |
| Cigar   | havana   | old-henry          | fonseca      | bluemaster  |
| House   | tower   | wooden      | colonial | gothic-revival |

